  "tag_line": "Water, layered air drying, full repair, then a 360 km/h launch",
  "description": "Drive a Gavril D-Series through a detailed Gridmap V2 car wash, or place the fully functional rigid structure from the Props vehicle selector on a flat surface in free roam. Standard and large vehicles, including the stock Wentward city bus, start five animated brushes, six water jets, and a layered mist, steam, and dust dryer. A midpoint restore cycle must complete before the fully contained 3-2-1-GO launch at 360 km/h, and the wash remains active until its final occupant exits.",
