  "update_summary": "Interior lighting pass: the rig grows from seven to thirteen shadowless lights (brighter cool-blue ceiling row, four warm-white wall task-fill points with emissive wall-pack fixtures, mirrored exit spotlights) and fixes a long-standing bug where light radius/range collapsed to one meter because the engine links light extent to object scale - the tunnel, entrance, and exit are now genuinely illuminated at night.",
